WEBVTT

00:01:29.125 --> 00:01:31.184
Gústanche as miñas mans?

00:01:31.208 --> 00:01:33.518
Son expresivas, non si?

00:01:33.542 --> 00:01:36.018
Agora mira as túas mans, adiante.

00:01:36.042 --> 00:01:38.726
Hai tanta historia grabada
a través do seu tacto

00:01:38.750 --> 00:01:43.309
E marcas do futuro 
debuxadas nas palmas

00:01:43.333 --> 00:01:45.143
Ás veces as mans agarran forte,

00:01:45.167 --> 00:01:47.958
outras veces deixan ir

00:01:49.375 --> 00:01:51.768
E se che dixese que

00:01:51.792 --> 00:01:54.292
todo se vai desfacer?

00:01:55.083 --> 00:01:56.476
Mmm

00:01:56.500 --> 00:01:58.226
Señoras e señores

00:01:58.250 --> 00:02:00.768
e os doutro xeito descrito